" content="Mould" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Easter" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="More effort" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Vegetarian" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Easter" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Celebration" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Indulgent" /></div></div><div class="recipe-header__description" itemprop="description"><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden method__content"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Make your own Easter eggs. It's much easier than you'd think and you can add personal touch.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="recipe-header__bottom"><div class="recipe-header__share service-links__container"><div class="service-links"><div class="service-label">Share:</div><ul class="service-links-primary"><li class="service-links-facebook first"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/5808/simple-chocolate-button-egg&amp;t=Simple%20chocolate%20button%20egg" title="Share on Facebook" class="service-links-facebook service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Facebook"><i class="font-icon font-icon-facebook-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Facebook</span></a></li><li class="service-links-pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/bookmarklet?media=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--560808_12.jpg&amp;url=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/5808/simple-chocolate-button-egg&amp;title=Simple%20chocolate%20button%20egg&amp;is_video=false&amp;description=" title="Pin it on Pinterest" class="service-links-pinterest service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Pinterest"><i class="font-icon font-icon-pinterest-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Pinterest</span></a></li><li class="service-links-twitter"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/5808/simple-chocolate-b